article_title: Austrian Court Denies U.S. Request to Extradite Dmytro Firtash
article_text:
An Austrian court refused to extradite a Ukrainian billionaire to the U.S., ruling that the federal bribery case against him was politically motivated.

Dmytro Firtash has accused the U.S. of trying to remove him from the political scene in Ukraine, where he was allied with the country’s recently ousted pro-Moscow president, Viktor...
